      • join

        public static java.lang.String join(java.util.List<java.lang.String> list,
                                    java.lang.String separator)
        字符串列表合并成字符串，以特定字符串作为分隔符 join list to string. if separator is null, use DEFAULT_JOIN_SEPARATOR 
         join(null, "#")     =   "";
 join({}, "#$")      =   "";
 join({a,b,c}, null) =   "a,b,c";
 join({a,b,c}, "")   =   "abc";
 join({a,b,c}, "#")  =   "a#b#c";
 join({a,b,c}, "#$") =   "a#$b#$c";
        参数:
        list -
        separator -
        返回:
        join list to string with separator. if list is empty, return ""
